this is not my mod but a mixture of mods that are realted to naruto.i have also added a save game which corrisponds with the mod.

featured mods = throwable shurikens
                       samehada
                       madara costume
                       flash step
                       unbound bow(since naruto has bows and arrows)
                       warglaive of azzinoth(world of warcraft mod but better with naruto)
